%% apps/flutter 架构图（Mermaid）
%% 可在支持 Mermaid 的编辑器或 VS Code 插件中预览

## 1. 应用分层架构

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Entry[入口层]
        Main[main.dart]
        Config[app_config.dart]
        Dotenv[flutter_dotenv]
    end

    subgraph Shell[应用壳]
        AppDart[app.dart]
        Router[GoRouter]
        Theme[MaterialApp_Material3]
    end

    subgraph UI[UI 层 screens]
        Login[login_screen]
        Dashboard[dashboard_screen]
        List[prompt_list_screen]
        Detail[prompt_detail_screen]
        Categories[categories_screen]
    end

    subgraph State[状态层 providers]
        AuthP[AuthProvider]
        PromptP[PromptProvider]
    end

    subgraph Service[服务层 services]
        Repo[PromptRepository]
        AI[AiService]
        Copy[CopyHistoryService]
    end

    subgraph Model[模型层 models]
        PromptM[prompt.dart]
        CatM[category.dart]
        VarM[variable.dart]
    end

    subgraph Remote[远端 Supabase]
        Auth[Auth]
        DB[(PostgreSQL)]
        Fn[optimize-prompt]
    end

    subgraph Local[本地存储]
        Prefs[SharedPreferences]
    end

    Main --> Config --> Dotenv
    Main --> AppDart --> Router --> Theme
    Router --> UI
    Main --> AuthP & PromptP
    UI --> AuthP & PromptP
    AuthP --> Auth
    PromptP --> Repo & AI
    Repo --> DB
    AI --> Fn
    Copy --> Prefs
    UI --> Copy
    Repo --> PromptM & CatM
    PromptM --> VarM
```

---

## 2. 认证与路由守卫

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Router as GoRouter
    participant Auth as AuthProvider
    participant SB as Supabase_Auth
    participant Login as LoginScreen
    participant Dash as DashboardScreen

    User->>Router: 打开应用
    Router->>Auth: isAuthenticated?
    alt 未登录
        Auth-->>Router: false
        Router->>Login: redirect /login
        User->>Login: 输入邮箱密码
        Login->>Auth: signIn()
        Auth->>SB: signInWithPassword
        SB-->>Auth: Session
        Auth->>Auth: notifyListeners()
        Router->>Router: refreshListenable 触发重定向
        Router->>Dash: redirect /
    else 已登录
        Auth-->>Router: true
        Router->>Dash: 进入首页
    end
```

