## 3. Prompt 数据流

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph Screen
        Dash[DashboardScreen]
        List[PromptListScreen]
        Detail[PromptDetailScreen]
    end

    subgraph Provider
        PP[PromptProvider]
    end

    subgraph Repository
        Repo[PromptRepository]
    end

    subgraph Supabase
        T1[(prompts)]
        T2[(categories)]
        Fn[optimize-prompt]
    end

    Dash -->|loadAll| PP
    List -->|search / delete / incrementUsage| PP
    Detail -->|create / update| PP
    Detail -->|optimizePrompt| AI[AiService]
    PP --> Repo
    Repo --> T1 & T2
    AI --> Fn
    PP -->|notifyListeners| Screen
```

---

## 4. 复制 Prompt 流程

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant List as PromptListScreen
    participant Clip as Clipboard
    participant Copy as CopyHistoryService
    participant PP as PromptProvider
    participant Repo as PromptRepository
    participant DB as Supabase

    User->>List: 点击复制
    List->>Clip: setData(content)
    List->>Copy: addEntry()
    Copy->>Copy: SharedPreferences 写入
    List->>PP: incrementUsage(id)
    PP->>Repo: usage_count + 1
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE prompts
    List->>User: SnackBar 提示
```

